<item>
            <title>[LU-6463] Interop 2.5.3&lt;-&gt;master ost-pools test_1c: Pool creation of testpool12345678 failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6463</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c3a03092-dfb8-11e4-b5b0-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c3a03092-dfb8-11e4-b5b0-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_1c failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Pool creation of testpool12345678 failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== ost-pools test 1c: Create a pool with a 16 character pool name == 04:23:32 (1428665012)
CMD: onyx-39vm3 lctl pool_new lustre.testpool12345678
onyx-39vm3: poolname testpool12345678 is too long (length is 16 max is 15)
onyx-39vm3: argument lustre.testpool12345678 must be &amp;lt;fsname&amp;gt;.&amp;lt;poolname&amp;gt;
onyx-39vm3: pool_new: File name too long
 ost-pools test_1c: @@@@@@ FAIL: Pool creation of testpool12345678 failed 
  Trace dump:
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: ost-pools 1c&lt;br/&gt;
Info required for matching: ost-pools 7b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
